                     </origPlace></creation><langUsage><language ident="de-x-enh" source="http://medieval-plants.org/mps-daten/inhalt/">Bavarian-Alemannic</language></langUsage></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body xml:space="preserve"><div type="recipe" xml:lang="de-x-enh" n="286" xml:id="bs1.286"> <title key="Pastry, a courtly">Von ainem hoefflichem <dish en="pastry" commodity="Q477248">gepachem</dish></title> <opener>Item ain hoefflichs <dish en="pastry" commodity="Q477248">pacheins</dish> mach also</opener> <instruction>ueber <alternative reason="tool">ain <tool en="mold" commodity="Q1941820">model</tool> oder <tool en="casserole" commodity="Q63436240">formm</tool> oder ueber ain <tool en="bowl" commodity="Q153988">schuessel</tool> <tool en="cup" commodity="Q81727">pecher</tool> oder <tool en="pot" commodity="Q15711817">hafen</tool> oder was du geren haben wild</alternative> aus ainem <ingredient en="dough" commodity="Q178024">taig mit <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayren</ingredient></ingredient> gemacht</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>steck <ingredient commodity="Q0" en="unsolved">zueegklach</ingredient> darein</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>legs dann auf ain <tool en="bowl" commodity="Q153988">schuessel</tool></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>mit <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">schmalcz</ingredient> gepachen</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>stecks an</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>nym <ingredient commodity="Q0" en="unsolved">roerlach</ingredient> als es gepachen ist</instruction>
 vnd <instruction>stecks vf die <ingredient commodity="Q0" en="unsolved">zueegklach</ingredient></instruction>
 vnd <instruction>thue <alternative reason="ingredient"><ingredient en="flower" commodity="Q506">pluemen</ingredient> oder <ingredient en="rose" commodity="Q34687">rosen</ingredient> oder was du wild</alternative> oben vf die <ingredient commodity="Q0" en="unsolved">roerlach</ingredient></instruction>
 <kitchenTip>Du machst ain essen machen In das <dish en="pastry" commodity="Q477248">gepachen</dish> wie du wild</kitchenTip> . </div></body></text></TEI>